<br>
Anyone noticed that recently they seem to be cleaning things up... long patches to fix framerate... crash problems etc... I mean all that extra income ... some  will go to fixing bug. (Sure they make some new ones, but give em a break, they are working with new technologie) Which will be fixed on other servers (yeah... they're gonna Just fix em on legends... right...).<br>
<br>
I don't see what people are getting so hot headed for? We are getting things that others are paying for (Don't tell them that).<br>
<br>
Incedently with my good friend Rhatha and the guild &quot;Chosen of Vah&quot; there is much better &quot;Events&quot; then any GM's have provided (though they try, god bless em). The only diffrence is that you don't get items from the guild events (well sometimes you do, but that's not the point).<br>
<br>
Ok... enough of that... <br>
That's my beleif for all those people who are getting all worked up over an &quot;Elite Server&quot;.<br>
<br>
Tirga<br>
